A cyberpunk cityscape at night where massive translucent holographic cubes float in the air, each containing different glowing data visualizations - one shows cascading spreadsheet cells, another displays flowing document streams, a third pulses with web browser wireframes. These containers are interconnected by bright neon data streams in electric blue and magenta, forming an intricate network against a dark sky filled with towering skyscrapers. The containers appear modular, clicking together like futuristic building blocks. Rain falls through the holographic projections, creating prismatic light refractions. In the foreground, reflective wet streets mirror the entire spectacle, doubling the visual complexity. The scene conveys assembly, modularity, and the seamless integration of diverse digital elements into one cohesive technological ecosystem.
